query:
INSERT INTO testimonials (clientName, clientTitle, rating, testimonialText, serviceUsed, featured, approved)
VALUES 
('Megan Dawson', NULL, 5, 'In regards to the work you did on my cover letter and resume, I couldn''t be happier. After years of using the same old resume and constantly adding to it, it was looking pretty ordinary. I wasn''t overly keen to spend money on a new one, but I''m happy I did. The layout was nice, not overdone, the information came out good once our emailing sessions had finished, and the cover letter was very well worded. Also, the added bonus of the 22 attached documents regarding interview tips and techniques was excellent. I have, and will recommend your business to the hundreds of colleagues I have and wish you success for the future. Keep up the good work.', NULL, 1, 1),
('Mayur Chauhan', NULL, 5, 'Sonia is amazing! I have been using her service for over 4 years.', NULL, 1, 1),
('Brad and Nichole Ralph', NULL, 5, 'Sonia''s attention to detail is outstanding. She meticulously crafted each bullet point, highlighting my most relevant accomplishments and quantifying my results. She also made sure my resume was visually appealing and easy to read. I''m thrilled with the final product!', NULL, 1, 1),
('Gavin Atkinson', NULL, 5, 'Professional and Excellent service. Sonia assisted in defining and creating a resume & cover letter that targeted my career aspirations. It got me an interview and now I have the job. Thank you Sonia!', NULL, 1, 1),
('Christina Paiva', NULL, 5, 'I knew I was way off the mark with my current Resume, now very pleased with the updated version from Sonia. Communication was excellent with updating details and the whole experience was very simple and taken care of professionally. Thoroughly recommend going through the process to ensure being up to date, and now there is further room to improve prospects with the additional services. Thank you so much Sonia & Team @ All Resume Services.', NULL, 1, 1)
